headline: Is Wynn Resorts (WYNN) Still Attractive After A 43.7% One Year Rally?
summary: If you are trying to work out whether Wynn Resorts is attractively priced or already fully reflecting investor optimism, you are in the right place. The stock last closed at US$116.40, with a 1 year return of 43.7% despite 7 day, 30 day and year to date declines of 3.4%, 5.9% and 5.0% respectively.
